---
---

<section id="about" class="section about">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">当院について</h2>
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="about-lead">
          お仕事帰りや夕方のお時間に、<br class="sp-only" />気軽に受診できるクリニックです。
        </p>
        <p class="about-description">
          生活習慣病など慢性疾患の継続的な管理から、急な発熱や体調不良への対応まで、<br />
          夕方以降のかかりつけ医として、お気軽にご相談ください。
        </p>
        <ul class="about-features">
          <li class="feature-item">
            <span class="feature-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
                <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <strong>夕方〜夜間診療</strong>
              <p>17:00〜21:00まで診療。お仕事帰りにも立ち寄れます。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            <span class="feature-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/>
                <line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/>
                <line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/>
                <line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <strong>土日も診療</strong>
              <p>平日だけでなく、土曜・日曜も診療を行っています。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            <span class="feature-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/>
                <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <strong>駅から徒歩2分</strong>
              <p>地下鉄南北線 勾当台公園駅から徒歩2分の好アクセス。</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="medical-area">
          <h3 class="medical-heading">診療内容</h3>
          <p class="medical-note">
            下記以外の症状もお気軽にご相談ください。必要に応じて専門医療機関へのご紹介も行います。
          </p>
          <div class="medical-columns">
            <div class="medical-card">
              <div class="medical-card-header">
                <span class="medical-card-icon">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/>
                  </svg>
                </span>
                <h4 class="medical-card-title">慢性疾患のかかりつけ</h4>
              </div>
              <p class="medical-card-description">
                夕方以降の時間帯で継続的に生活習慣病などの管理・治療を行います。
              </p>
              <ul class="condition-list">
                <li class="condition-tag">高血圧</li>
                <li class="condition-tag">糖尿病</li>
                <li class="condition-tag">脂質異常症</li>
                <li class="condition-tag">高尿酸血症・痛風</li>
                <li class="condition-tag">甲状腺疾患</li>
                <li class="condition-tag">貧血</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="medical-card">
              <div class="medical-card-header">
                <span class="medical-card-icon">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <line x1="12" y1="2" x2="12" y2="22"/>
                    <line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/>
                  </svg>
                </span>
                <h4 class="medical-card-title">夜間の急な症状にも対応</h4>
              </div>
              <p class="medical-card-description">
                夕方以降の急な発熱や体調不良に対応します。
              </p>
              <ul class="condition-list">
                <li class="condition-tag">発熱・感冒症状</li>
                <li class="condition-tag">咳・喉の痛み</li>
                <li class="condition-tag">腹痛・下痢・嘔吐</li>
                <li class="condition-tag">花粉症・アレルギー</li>
                <li class="condition-tag">頻尿・排尿時痛</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: white;
  }

  .about-content {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-lead {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  .about-description {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    line-height: 1.9;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .about-features {
    display: grid;
    gap: 28px;
  }

  .feature-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 18px;
    padding: 24px;
    background: var(--color-bg-warm);
    border-radius: 4px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--color-navy-medium);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .feature-item strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .feature-item p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .medical-area {
    margin-top: 64px;
  }

  .medical-heading {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .medical-columns {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .medical-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-blue);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 28px 24px;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--color-navy);
  }

  .medical-card-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .medical-card-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--color-navy-medium);
  }

  .medical-card-title {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .medical-card-description {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .condition-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .condition-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 5px 12px;
    background: white;
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    border-radius: 3px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .medical-note {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .sp-only {
    display: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .sp-only {
      display: inline;
    }

    .about-lead {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .about-description {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .feature-item {
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .feature-icon svg {
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
    }

    .medical-area {
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    .medical-heading {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .medical-columns {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 28px;
    }

    .medical-card {
      padding: 22px 18px;
    }

    .medical-card-title {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .condition-tag {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      padding: 3px 8px;
    }

    .medical-note {
      text-align: left;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  }
</style>
